Add Lipid properties

Source: R/data_processing.R
addLipidProperties.Rd

Based on lipid column

addLipidProperties(
  data,
  lipidClassOrder = c("PC", "PC O-", "LPC", "PE", "PE O-", "PE P-", "LPE", "PS",
    "PS O-", "PI", "PI O-", "PG", "PG O-", "LPG", "PA", "PA O-", "LPA", "CL", "MLCL",
    "Cer", "SM", "HexCer", "SGalCer", "GM3", "Sulf", "diHexCer", "Hex2Cer", "For", "IPC",
    "MIPC", "M(IP)2C", "Chol", "Desm", "Erg", "CE", "EE", "DAG", "TAG", "PIP", "PIP2",
    "PIP3", "GM1Cer", "GD1Cer", "MAG", "Epi", "PGP", "WE", "FA")
)

Arguments

data

tibble. rawData
lipidClassOrder

character vector, order of lipid classes

Value

tibble. enhanced data
